messages.messageBody:
Are there people here from Michigan? I've writtent the Michigan
Unschoolers list, but there's not much time left.

I'm to be interviewed June 3/Thursday by phone, on a talk show in
Michigan. Scott Winter and Michelle McCormick, "Mouth 2 Mouth with
Scott and Michelle.

Here are the links I was sent and one of them should have a phone
number and such:

Melissa Limber
Producer
"Mouth 2 Mouth with Scott and Michelle"
9A-Noon
Newsradio WOOD 1300
www.woodradio.com
They're calling me at 9:35.

I would be happy to have someone (or several) from Michigan call in
and give them real, local information.

I wish I had known about it all sooner, but I was travelling all day
today and didn't check e-mail until I had gotten to Quebec, and to
Bea's house (where Holly lives) and had a house tour and a nap. So
not much notice.

Sandra
